Self-starter.
Motivated to meet individual as well as team targets.
ASSOCIATE, MIDDLE MARKET  EPMI West Power Trading in Portland, Oregon seeks an Associate to work in the Middle Market Group.
This individual will support Commercial level managers and directors with the Middle Market Group to manage physical energy purchases and sales and market structured financial products to utility and large industrial customers in the western United States.
